-> The instruction is about how to report a bug. 
-> The title of the bug report should be clear and concise, and it should include the name of the product or service that the bug is affecting.
-> The body of the bug report should include a clear and concise description of the bug, as well as steps to reproduce the bug. If applicable, the bug report should also include screenshots or other attachments that can help to explain the problem.
-> The bug report should also include information about the user's operating system, browser, and version. This information can help the development team to reproduce the bug and fix it.
